sequenceDiagram
    participant Orch as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant BuiltIn as Built-in Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant Judge as LLM Judge Detector<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    participant S3 as S3/MinIO<br/>9000/TCP HTTP
    participant vLLM as vLLM Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

    Note over S3,HFHub: Startup Phase (Model Loading)

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over HF,HFHub: Flow 2 - Step 0: Model Initialization
        HFHub-->>S3: Model uploaded to S3/MinIO
        Note over HF,S3: KServe Storage Initializer
        S3->>HF: Download model files<br/>AWS credentials<br/>HTTP 9000/TCP
        Note over HF: Load model into memory<br/>(GPU via CUDA or CPU)
    end

    Note over Orch,vLLM: Runtime Phase (Detection Requests)

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Orch,BuiltIn: Flow 1: Content Detection (Built-in)
        Orch->>BuiltIn: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Istio mTLS<br/>KServe platform auth
        Note over BuiltIn: Local processing:<br/>- Regex PII detection<br/>- File-type validation<br/>- Custom Python detectors
        BuiltIn-->>Orch: Detection results<br/>[{detection, score}]<br/>Istio mTLS
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Orch,S3: Flow 2: Content Detection (HuggingFace)
        Orch->>HF: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Istio mTLS<br/>KServe platform auth
        Note over HF: Local PyTorch inference:<br/>- SeqClassification OR<br/>- GraniteCausalLM<br/>(GPU or CPU)
        HF-->>Orch: Detection results<br/>[{detection, score}]<br/>Istio mTLS
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over Orch,vLLM: Flow 3: Content Detection (LLM Judge)
        Orch->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Istio mTLS<br/>KServe platform auth
        Judge->>vLLM: LLM evaluation request<br/>OpenAI-compatible API<br/>HTTP 8080/TCP (in-cluster)
        vLLM-->>Judge: Evaluation result<br/>HTTP
        Judge-->>Orch: Detection results<br/>[{detection, score}]<br/>Istio mTLS
    end

    rect rgb(255, 255, 240)
        Note over Orch,Judge: Flow 3 Alt: Generation Analysis (LLM Judge only)
        Orch->>Judge: POST /api/v1/text/generation<br/>Istio mTLS<br/>{prompt + response pair}
        Judge->>vLLM: Evaluate prompt+response<br/>OpenAI-compatible API
        vLLM-->>Judge: Evaluation scores
        Judge-->>Orch: Generation analysis results<br/>Istio mTLS
    end
